race.comment: ARTFUL PERSUASION (7) tough gelding with his hoof on the till fifth-up. Should get the required tempo for this after charging late with a game third over 1600m at Kembla Grange in BM64 class. Key jockey change from the good barrier and can race closer. Each way. KINGSTON CHARM (9) another who looks to get the right set up today. Chipped away late with the 58kg when a narrow seventh over 1600m at Warwick Farm. Gets further weight relief and has the figures to take this out. SATNESS (4) collared late with the 59kg when second to the progressive Cuban Cigar over 1400m at Kembla Grange. Should go well up on the speed. ZENMASTER (6) back to his pet trip and stays in the mix.
